flowRoot.flowPara: The avatars are generated with the initials of the user's name.
There are 8 different color variants, which consist of a vertical gradient along the entire height and a matching tinted foreground color.
If there are more than two names we use
the initials of the first two.
If there's only one name we only use one letter.
In this case the font size can be a bit larger at small
If there's no name we use
At smaller sizes the text is pure white, larger compared to the
overall circle size, and ultra bold.
At larger sizes (>40px) the text is tinted, smaller compared to
the overall circle size, and bold.
